r the hotel, about $20 ala carte dinners. The Farro e Cinghiale  (Braised wild boar) is wonderful! (1031 S Rampart Blvd)- Hennesseys - burgers and fries (Freemont Street)- Ricardos - a local favorite for Mexican food (4930 W Flamingo Rd)	
