y. The strip is 20-30 mins away. After seeing some of the crowded strip hotels I was so glad we stayed at this beautiful hotel. We were traveling with a little one and wanted to relax. If you were coming in for a night or something this is not the place. You need a little time to ejoy your surroundings. I asked for a late check out on the last day because I was a Marriott Rewards member we did not have to check out until 3pm. Worst part of our trip was the flight. I will never fly Jet Blue again. It is not worth the discounted fare for that long of a flight (from NY).	
